For me this is THE long awaited Android mobile / portable / general contest log. Easy to use, set up, edit and exports in the required formats with ease and has many more useful features. No more dragging a laptop or paper log around when operating portable or backpacking. I've used this in the last 4 contests 2m AFS, and 3 UKAC's since downloading it last week and it is spot on.
